The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-09-2013 FRI





....THE OTHER ONE SAID AUG-08 FRI....FRI IS AUG 09....SAME SHOW.....



















The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET



  Today on the program Glenn talks personnel shifts at FOX News and MSNBC.

  FOX could be losing Sean Hannity and MSNBC is going to have a new show featuring Alec Baldwin.

  Also today is the IRS still targeting Tea Party groups?
